(7, 14, 'en', 'Privacy policy', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">General Terms and Conditions</span></p>\n<h1><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\"> </span></h1>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">General Terms and Conditions are an integral part of the Package Travel Contract concluded between the Agency as the travel organizer on one side and the Traveler as the contracting party on the other side. In addition to these General Terms, the Contract also includes the Travel Package Program. If specified by the Contract and/or the Travel Package Program, Special Terms and Conditions are also integral parts of the Contract, in addition to these General Terms. In the event of any discrepancies between the Contract, the Travel Package Program, the Special Terms and Conditions, and these General Terms, the order of precedence shall be as follows: the Contract, the Travel Package Program, the Special Terms and Conditions, and finally, the General Terms.</span></p>\n<h1><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\"> </span></h1>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">These General Terms apply only to package tours where the Agency is the organizer. Therefore, these General Terms do not apply in cases where the Agency acts as an intermediary and/or sells services from other travel agencies. If the Agency acts as an intermediary and/or sells services from other travel agencies, the Contract will specify the responsible travel organizer, and the general terms of that organizer will apply, which the Agency will make available to the Traveler. These General Terms are considered applicable if the Contract does not specify otherwise.</span></p>\n<h1><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\"> </span></h1>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Content of the Arrangement</span></p>\n<h1><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\"> </span></h1>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">The organizer of your trip guarantees the implementation of the program as described in the arrangement program that they organize and that you have received. The content of the arrangement will be fully realized as described unless exceptional circumstances (war, riots, strikes, terrorist actions, sanitary disturbances, natural disasters, interventions by competent authorities, transport delays, epidemics, and pandemics) prevent it.</span></p>\n<h1><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\"> </span></h1>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Applications and Payments</span></p>\n<h1><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\"> </span></h1>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Applications for travel are accepted through the website or directly to the account of the Travel Organizer. When applying, the Passenger is obliged to provide accurate personal information for all passengers, i.e., persons listed in the reservation as they appear in travel documents that passengers will use during the trip or reservation consumption, and to provide all documentation necessary for the organization of the trip, all in accordance with the Regulation (EU) 2016/679 of the European Parliament and of the Council of 27 April 2016 on the protection of natural persons with regard to the processing of personal data and on the free movement of such data and the Law on the Implementation of the General Data Protection Regulation. As a travel agency, the Organizer guarantees that all documents and valid data necessary for the smooth execution of the trip will be used in accordance with legal regulations arising from the Contract and the General Terms. The Organizer is not responsible for the use or forwarding of incorrect or incomplete personal data of persons listed in the reservation, and all costs incurred due to incorrect or incomplete personal data of persons listed in the reservation will be borne by the Passenger.</span></p>\n<h1><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\"> </span></h1>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">When applying for group trips, the Passenger pays 30% of the value of the arrangement, and the remaining amount must be paid 45 days before the trip unless otherwise specified. When applying for individual trips, the Passenger pays the full amount of the arrangement according to the specified deadlines. On the day of application, the Passenger signs the contract under the title \"I am familiar with the program and terms of travel and accept them in full. I confirm that I have been offered travel insurance.\" In this way, everything mentioned in these terms becomes a legal obligation for both the Passenger and the Organizer.</span></p>\n<h1><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\"> </span></h1>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Content and Price of the Arrangement</span></p>\n<h1><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\"> </span></h1>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">The content of the arrangement includes everything that the Travel Organizer has stated in the travel program. Special services are services not included in the price of the arrangement and are therefore paid separately by the Passenger. These services should be requested when applying and are paid to the Tourism Companion or the representative of the Travel Organizer in the currency of the country where the service is provided. The prices of the arrangements are published in euros, calculated according to the prices of services in reference currencies at the exchange rate of the Organizer\'s bank on a specific day. The Organizer reserves the right to change the published prices in case of changes in accommodation prices, meals, transportation, and other services, or in case of changes in the exchange rate of the currencies that are the basis for calculating the arrangement price. For an increase in the arrangement price and additional content of up to 8%, no consent of the Passenger is required (the increase is calculated on all parts of the payment). In case of an increase greater than 8%, the Passenger has the right to terminate the contract without the obligation to compensate for the damage.</span></p>\n<h1><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\"> </span></h1>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">In case of unoccupied but reserved capacities on individual arrangements, the Organizer reserves the right to adjust the price and apply special marketing activities to facilitate the sale of unoccupied capacities. Passengers who have paid the full price of the arrangement are not entitled to a refund of the price difference.</span></p>\n<h1><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\"> </span></h1>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Categorization and Description of Services</span></p>\n<h1><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\"> </span></h1>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Offered accommodation facilities, restaurants, means of transportation, etc., are described according to the official categorization of the local tourist organization at the time of issuing the program. Standards of accommodation, meals, services, etc., in different places vary and are not comparable. The Organizer is not responsible for oral or written information that does not comply with the description of services and facilities in published programs and is obtained from a third party. If a Passenger uses a triple or quadruple room in a hotel, the hotelier usually provides a double room with an extra bed or a room with two double beds for accommodation for 4 persons. The quality of the extra (additional) bed depends entirely on the hotel. In any case, the Organizer is not responsible for the quality of the extra bed, so any dissatisfaction of the Passenger arising from these reasons cannot be the subject of a complaint.</span></p>\n<h1><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\"> </span></h1>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Change of Program</span></p>\n<h1><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\"> </span></h1>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">The travel organizer has the right to change the program if extraordinary circumstances occur (cancellations, delays, changes by local agencies) that cannot be foreseen, avoided, or eliminated. The schedule of visits during the trip is subject to change at the discretion of the tour guide. The agreed accommodation can only be replaced with accommodation in an object of the same or higher category, at the expense of the Organizer, and it will be considered that it has been fully implemented. If changes in the package travel contract or a replacement package travel contract result in a package travel of lower quality or price, the Passenger has the right to an appropriate price reduction.</span></p>\n<h1><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\"> </span></h1>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Right of the Organizer to Cancel</span></p>\n<h1><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\"> </span></h1>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">The Organizer may terminate the package travel contract before the start of the package travel and return all payments received for the package travel to the Passenger in full, without the obligation to compensate for any damage to the Passenger:</span></p>\n<h1><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\"> </span></h1>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">If extraordinary circumstances that could not be avoided prevent the Organizer from performing the contract, and if the Organizer informs the Passenger of the termination of the contract without undue delay before the start of the package travel.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">If the number of persons registered for the package travel is less than the minimum number specified in the contract, and if the Organizer informs the Passenger of the termination of the contract within the deadline specified in the contract, but not later than at least 20 days before the start of the package travel.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Passenger\'s Cancellation of the Trip</span></p>\n<h1><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\"> </span></h1>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">The Passenger has the right to cancel the trip orally or in writing before the start of the trip at the sales point where the trip was registered. In that case, the Organizer has the right to compensation for the canceled trip, and the amount of the costs is determined according to the day of the Passenger\'s cancellation and the type of travel. For all of the above, the Organizer suggests travel insurance. If the Passenger cancels the paid arrangement, the Organizer retains:</span></p>\n<h1><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\"> </span></h1>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Long-distance travel (outside Europe):</span></p>\n<h1><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\"> </span></h1>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">For cancellation up to 180 days before departure: 20%</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">For cancellation 179-90 days before departure: 70%</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">For cancellation 89-0 days before departure and after departure: 100%</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Individual travel, airline tickets, and accommodation reservations:</span></p>\n<h1><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\"> </span></h1>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">If the Passenger cancels an individual package arrangement that includes an airline ticket and accommodation, the Organizer retains 100% of the total price of the airline ticket as compensation (unless otherwise stated in the airline ticket tariff) regardless of the time until the start of the trip, and for the cancellation of hotels and other services, the conditions of the suppliers apply unless the service is reserved under special conditions that do not allow a refund (so-called non-refundable) when the service provider retains 100% of the amount of the service.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">The Organizer is obliged to ensure the implementation of services as well as the choice of service providers with the care of a good organizer and to take care of the rights and interests of the Passenger in accordance with good practices in tourism. The Organizer undertakes to provide all the services listed for a particular arrangement in the program and is responsible to the Passenger for any failure to perform services or part of the services. In these cases, the Passenger bears all additional costs.</span></p>\n<h1><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\"> </span></h1>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Passenger\'s Obligations</span></p>\n<h1><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\"> </span></h1>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">The Passenger is obliged to:</span></p>\n<h1><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\"> </span></h1>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Possess valid travel documents and provide names and surnames as they appear in the document (passport) with which they are traveling. At the request of the Organizer, the Passenger is obliged to provide a copy or original of the valid passport that they will use during the trip. For subsequent changes or additions to surnames, the Passenger bears the costs of change and modification. For long-distance travel (outside Europe), the passport must be valid for at least 6 months from the entry into the country. The cost of loss or theft of documents during the trip is borne by the Passenger. The Companion or the representative of the Organizer will assist, but subject to the smooth running of the program. If a visa is required for any trip, the Travel Organizer may, at the request of the Passenger, when possible, mediate in obtaining it for a fee. The Travel Organizer does not guarantee the issuance of visas and is not responsible for their correctness.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Vaccinate and possess certificates and documents for vaccinations for travel to countries where it is required according to the regulations of the World Health Organization. In this case, the Passenger submits a medical certificate. The lack of these documents or the invalidity of travel documents that lead to cancellation of the trip or the inability to continue the trip do not obligate the Travel Organizer and cancellation costs are charged according to Article 7.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Comply with customs and foreign exchange regulations of the Republic of Croatia, as well as the countries visited during the trip.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Adhere to the house rules in all visited facilities and cooperate with service providers in good faith.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Follow the instructions and cooperate with the Organizer, tour guide, and/or the Organizer\'s representative. When departing on a trip, the Passenger must present a document confirming the paid arrangement (original voucher, payment confirmation, copy of the payment order).</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Request and check all received travel documents (airline tickets, hotel vouchers, insurance policies, transfer schedules, etc.). If the Organizer does not receive a note from the Passenger within 24 hours (or as specified in the offer) after the documents are delivered, it will be considered that all sent documentation is valid and correct, and all costs of changes and modifications will be borne by the Passenger.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">In cases of non-compliance with these obligations, the Passenger is liable to the Organizer for any damage caused.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Luggage</span></p>\n<h1><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\"> </span></h1>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Unless otherwise specified in the travel program, the Passenger is entitled to free transportation of up to 15 kg of luggage on charter flights and up to 20 kg of luggage on regular flights. Children under 2 years of age are not entitled to free luggage transportation. Luggage is transported at the risk of the Passenger, so it is recommended to insure the luggage with an insurance company. The Travel Organizer is not responsible for damaged or lost luggage, theft of luggage or valuables in hotels (safe rental is recommended), or means of transportation. In case of damaged or lost luggage, the Passenger should report it to the carrier or the reception of the accommodation facility, depending on where the damage or loss occurred.</span></p>\n<h1><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\"> </span></h1>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Travel Insurance</span></p>\n<h1><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\"> </span></h1>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Employees of the agency where the arrangement is paid are obliged to offer the Passenger a \"package\" of travel insurance consisting of passenger health insurance during their stay abroad, luggage insurance, accident insurance, as well as insurance against the risk of the Passenger\'s trip cancellation, which are offered for both trips abroad and within our country. The insurance policy against the risk of the Passenger\'s trip cancellation must be issued no later than 48 hours from the first payment. By accepting the travel contract, which includes these travel conditions, the Passenger confirms that the \"package\" of travel insurance was offered to them. The Travel Organizer acts as an intermediary when arranging an insurance policy, and in the event of a claim against the insurance company, they cannot influence the outcome.</span></p>\n<h1><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\"> </span></h1>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Accommodation in Rooms/Apartments</span></p>\n<h1><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\"> </span></h1>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">If the Passenger has not explicitly agreed to a room/apartment with specific characteristics, they will accept any officially registered room/apartment for rent in that facility, as described in the catalog and price list. If possible, the Organizer will try to meet the Passenger\'s additional accommodation request (comfort, room orientation, floor, etc.), but cannot guarantee the fulfillment of such a request.</span></p>\n<h1><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\"> </span></h1>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Travel Organized by Other Organizers/Tour Operators</span></p>\n<h1><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\"> </span></h1>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">For all arrangements where Desert Road for Tourism is the main organizer, these General Terms apply, except in cases where Desert Road for Tourism is an intermediary and is not the main organizer of the trip. For such arrangements, the responsible organizer will be indicated in the Contract, and the general terms of the responsible organizer apply to that trip, and Desert Road for Tourism is not responsible for the execution of travel arrangements by other organizers. By signing the contract, the Passenger fully accepts the program and travel conditions.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\"> </span></p>', NULL, 1, 1, '2023-08-31 06:12:46', '2023-09-07 10:25:57');
INSERT INTO `core_page_translations` (`id`, `origin_id`, `locale`, `title`, `content`, `short_desc`, `create_user`, `update_user`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(8, 15, 'en', 'Terms and Conditions', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">General Terms and Conditions</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span> </span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">General Terms and Conditions are an integral part of the Package Travel Contract concluded between the Agency as the travel organizer on one side and the Traveler as the contracting party on the other side. In addition to these General Terms, the Contract also includes the Travel Package Program. If specified by the Contract and/or the Travel Package Program, Special Terms and Conditions are also integral parts of the Contract, in addition to these General Terms. In the event of any discrepancies between the Contract, the Travel Package Program, the Special Terms and Conditions, and these General Terms, the order of precedence shall be as follows: the Contract, the Travel Package Program, the Special Terms and Conditions, and finally, the General Terms.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">These General Terms apply only to package tours where the Agency is the organizer. Therefore, these General Terms do not apply in cases where the Agency acts as an intermediary and/or sells services from other travel agencies. If the Agency acts as an intermediary and/or sells services from other travel agencies, the Contract will specify the responsible travel organizer, and the general terms of that organizer will apply, which the Agency will make available to the Traveler. These General Terms are considered applicable if the Contract does not specify otherwise.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Content of the Arrangement</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">The organizer of your trip guarantees the implementation of the program as described in the arrangement program that they organize and that you have received. The content of the arrangement will be fully realized as described unless exceptional circumstances (war, riots, strikes, terrorist actions, sanitary disturbances, natural disasters, interventions by competent authorities, transport delays, epidemics, and pandemics) prevent it.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Applications and Payments</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Applications for travel are accepted through the website or directly to the account of the Travel Organizer. When applying, the Passenger is obliged to provide accurate personal information for all passengers, i.e., persons listed in the reservation as they appear in travel documents that passengers will use during the trip or reservation consumption, and to provide all documentation necessary for the organization of the trip, all in accordance with the Regulation (EU) 2016/679 of the European Parliament and of the Council of 27 April 2016 on the protection of natural persons with regard to the processing of personal data and on the free movement of such data and the Law on the Implementation of the General Data Protection Regulation. As a travel agency, the Organizer guarantees that all documents and valid data necessary for the smooth execution of the trip will be used in accordance with legal regulations arising from the Contract and the General Terms. The Organizer is not responsible for the use or forwarding of incorrect or incomplete personal data of persons listed in the reservation, and all costs incurred due to incorrect or incomplete personal data of persons listed in the reservation will be borne by the Passenger.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">When applying for group trips, the Passenger pays 30% of the value of the arrangement, and the remaining amount must be paid 45 days before the trip unless otherwise specified. When applying for individual trips, the Passenger pays the full amount of the arrangement according to the specified deadlines. On the day of application, the Passenger signs the contract under the title \"I am familiar with the program and terms of travel and accept them in full. I confirm that I have been offered travel insurance.\" In this way, everything mentioned in these terms becomes a legal obligation for both the Passenger and the Organizer.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Content and Price of the Arrangement</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">The content of the arrangement includes everything that the Travel Organizer has stated in the travel program. Special services are services not included in the price of the arrangement and are therefore paid separately by the Passenger. These services should be requested when applying and are paid to the Tourism Companion or the representative of the Travel Organizer in the currency of the country where the service is provided. The prices of the arrangements are published in euros, calculated according to the prices of services in reference currencies at the exchange rate of the Organizer\'s bank on a specific day. The Organizer reserves the right to change the published prices in case of changes in accommodation prices, meals, transportation, and other services, or in case of changes in the exchange rate of the currencies that are the basis for calculating the arrangement price. For an increase in the arrangement price and additional content of up to 8%, no consent of the Passenger is required (the increase is calculated on all parts of the payment). In case of an increase greater than 8%, the Passenger has the right to terminate the contract without the obligation to compensate for the damage.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">In case of unoccupied but reserved capacities on individual arrangements, the Organizer reserves the right to adjust the price and apply special marketing activities to facilitate the sale of unoccupied capacities. Passengers who have paid the full price of the arrangement are not entitled to a refund of the price difference.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Categorization and Description of Services</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Offered accommodation facilities, restaurants, means of transportation, etc., are described according to the official categorization of the local tourist organization at the time of issuing the program. Standards of accommodation, meals, services, etc., in different places vary and are not comparable. The Organizer is not responsible for oral or written information that does not comply with the description of services and facilities in published programs and is obtained from a third party. If a Passenger uses a triple or quadruple room in a hotel, the hotelier usually provides a double room with an extra bed or a room with two double beds for accommodation for 4 persons. The quality of the extra (additional) bed depends entirely on the hotel. In any case, the Organizer is not responsible for the quality of the extra bed, so any dissatisfaction of the Passenger arising from these reasons cannot be the subject of a complaint.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Change of Program</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">The travel organizer has the right to change the program if extraordinary circumstances occur (cancellations, delays, changes by local agencies) that cannot be foreseen, avoided, or eliminated. The schedule of visits during the trip is subject to change at the discretion of the tour guide. The agreed accommodation can only be replaced with accommodation in an object of the same or higher category, at the expense of the Organizer, and it will be considered that it has been fully implemented. If changes in the package travel contract or a replacement package travel contract result in a package travel of lower quality or price, the Passenger has the right to an appropriate price reduction.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Right of the Organizer to Cancel</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">The Organizer may terminate the package travel contract before the start of the package travel and return all payments received for the package travel to the Passenger in full, without the obligation to compensate for any damage to the Passenger:</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">If extraordinary circumstances that could not be avoided prevent the Organizer from performing the contract, and if the Organizer informs the Passenger of the termination of the contract without undue delay before the start of the package travel.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">If the number of persons registered for the package travel is less than the minimum number specified in the contract, and if the Organizer informs the Passenger of the termination of the contract within the deadline specified in the contract, but not later than at least 20 days before the start of the package travel.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Passenger\'s Cancellation of the Trip</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">The Passenger has the right to cancel the trip orally or in writing before the start of the trip at the sales point where the trip was registered. In that case, the Organizer has the right to compensation for the canceled trip, and the amount of the costs is determined according to the day of the Passenger\'s cancellation and the type of travel. For all of the above, the Organizer suggests travel insurance. If the Passenger cancels the paid arrangement, the Organizer retains:</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Long-distance travel (outside Europe):</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">For cancellation up to 180 days before departure: 20%</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">For cancellation 179-90 days before departure: 70%</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">For cancellation 89-0 days before departure and after departure: 100%</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Individual travel, airline tickets, and accommodation reservations:</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">If the Passenger cancels an individual package arrangement that includes an airline ticket and accommodation, the Organizer retains 100% of the total price of the airline ticket as compensation (unless otherwise stated in the airline ticket tariff) regardless of the time until the start of the trip, and for the cancellation of hotels and other services, the conditions of the suppliers apply unless the service is reserved under special conditions that do not allow a refund (so-called non-refundable) when the service provider retains 100% of the amount of the service.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">The Organizer is obliged to ensure the implementation of services as well as the choice of service providers with the care of a good organizer and to take care of the rights and interests of the Passenger in accordance with good practices in tourism. The Organizer undertakes to provide all the services listed for a particular arrangement in the program and is responsible to the Passenger for any failure to perform services or part of the services. In these cases, the Passenger bears all additional costs.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Passenger\'s Obligations</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">The Passenger is obliged to:</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Possess valid travel documents and provide names and surnames as they appear in the document (passport) with which they are traveling. At the request of the Organizer, the Passenger is obliged to provide a copy or original of the valid passport that they will use during the trip. For subsequent changes or additions to surnames, the Passenger bears the costs of change and modification. For long-distance travel (outside Europe), the passport must be valid for at least 6 months from the entry into the country. The cost of loss or theft of documents during the trip is borne by the Passenger. The Companion or the representative of the Organizer will assist, but subject to the smooth running of the program. If a visa is required for any trip, the Travel Organizer may, at the request of the Passenger, when possible, mediate in obtaining it for a fee. The Travel Organizer does not guarantee the issuance of visas and is not responsible for their correctness.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Vaccinate and possess certificates and documents for vaccinations for travel to countries where it is required according to the regulations of the World Health Organization. In this case, the Passenger submits a medical certificate. The lack of these documents or the invalidity of travel documents that lead to cancellation of the trip or the inability to continue the trip do not obligate the Travel Organizer and cancellation costs are charged according to Article 7.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Comply with customs and foreign exchange regulations of the Republic of Croatia, as well as the countries visited during the trip.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Adhere to the house rules in all visited facilities and cooperate with service providers in good faith.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Follow the instructions and cooperate with the Organizer, tour guide, and/or the Organizer\'s representative. When departing on a trip, the Passenger must present a document confirming the paid arrangement (original voucher, payment confirmation, copy of the payment order).</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Request and check all received travel documents (airline tickets, hotel vouchers, insurance policies, transfer schedules, etc.). If the Organizer does not receive a note from the Passenger within 24 hours (or as specified in the offer) after the documents are delivered, it will be considered that all sent documentation is valid and correct, and all costs of changes and modifications will be borne by the Passenger.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">In cases of non-compliance with these obligations, the Passenger is liable to the Organizer for any damage caused.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Luggage</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Unless otherwise specified in the travel program, the Passenger is entitled to free transportation of up to 15 kg of luggage on charter flights and up to 20 kg of luggage on regular flights. Children under 2 years of age are not entitled to free luggage transportation. Luggage is transported at the risk of the Passenger, so it is recommended to insure the luggage with an insurance company. The Travel Organizer is not responsible for damaged or lost luggage, theft of luggage or valuables in hotels (safe rental is recommended), or means of transportation. In case of damaged or lost luggage, the Passenger should report it to the carrier or the reception of the accommodation facility, depending on where the damage or loss occurred.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Travel Insurance</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Employees of the agency where the arrangement is paid are obliged to offer the Passenger a \"package\" of travel insurance consisting of passenger health insurance during their stay abroad, luggage insurance, accident insurance, as well as insurance against the risk of the Passenger\'s trip cancellation, which are offered for both trips abroad and within our country. The insurance policy against the risk of the Passenger\'s trip cancellation must be issued no later than 48 hours from the first payment. By accepting the travel contract, which includes these travel conditions, the Passenger confirms that the \"package\" of travel insurance was offered to them. The Travel Organizer acts as an intermediary when arranging an insurance policy, and in the event of a claim against the insurance company, they cannot influence the outcome.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Accommodation in Rooms/Apartments</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">If the Passenger has not explicitly agreed to a room/apartment with specific characteristics, they will accept any officially registered room/apartment for rent in that facility, as described in the catalog and price list. If possible, the Organizer will try to meet the Passenger\'s additional accommodation request (comfort, room orientation, floor, etc.), but cannot guarantee the fulfillment of such a request.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Travel Organized by Other Organizers/Tour Operators</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">For all arrangements where Desert Road for Tourism is the main organizer, these General Terms apply, except in cases where Desert Road for Tourism is an intermediary and is not the main organizer of the trip. For such arrangements, the responsible organizer will be indicated in the Contract, and the general terms of the responsible organizer apply to that trip, and Desert Road for Tourism is not responsible for the execution of travel arrangements by other organizers. By signing the contract, the Passenger fully accepts the program and travel conditions.</span></p>', NULL, 1, 1, '2023-09-07 10:27:41', '2023-09-07 10:47:56');
INSERT INTO `core_page_translations` (`id`, `origin_id`, `locale`, `title`, `content`, `short_desc`, `create_user`, `update_user`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(9, 15, 'hr', 'Terms and Conditions', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Opći uvjeti poslovanja</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;text-align:justify;margin-top:14pt;margin-bottom:14pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#1c2216;vertical-align:baseline;\">Opći uvjeti poslovanja sastavni su dio Ugovora o putovanju u paket-aranžmanu sklopljenog između Agencije kao organizatora putovanja s jedne strane i Ugovaratelja putovanja s druge strane.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;text-align:justify;margin-top:14pt;margin-bottom:14pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#1c2216;vertical-align:baseline;\">Uz ove Opće uvjete, sastavni dio Ugovora čini i Program putovanja u paket-aranžmanu. Kada je to Ugovorom i/ili Programom putovanja naznačeno, sastavni dio Ugovora, uz ove Opće uvjete, čine i Posebni uvjeti poslovanja.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;text-align:justify;margin-top:14pt;margin-bottom:14pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#1c2216;vertical-align:baseline;\">U slučaju da je Ugovorom i/ili Programom putovanja i/ili Posebnim uvjetima, a u vezi bilo koje od točaka ovih Općih uvjeta određeno drugačije, vrijedi redom ono određeno Ugovorom, potom Programom putovanja, zatim Posebnim uvjetima te najzad Općim uvjetima.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;text-align:justify;margin-top:14pt;margin-bottom:14pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#1c2216;vertical-align:baseline;\">Opći uvjeti vrijede samo za paket-aranžmane u kojima je Agencija organizator. Stoga se ovi Opći uvjeti ne primjenjuju u slučaju da Agencija posreduje i/ili prodaje usluge drugih turističkih agencija. U slučaju da Agencija posreduje i/ili prodaje usluge drugih turističkih agencija, u Ugovoru će biti naznačen odgovorni organizator putovanja te će se primjenjivati opći uvjeti tog organizatora a koje će Agencija učiniti dostupnima Ugovaratelju. Smatra se da se primjenjuju Opći uvjeti Agencije ako u Ugovoru nije drugačije određeno.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span> </span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;vertical-align:baseline;\">Sadržaj aranžmana</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;background-color:#ffffff;vertical-align:baseline;\">Organizator vašeg putovanja jamči provedbu programa prema opisu aranžmana u programu koji on organizira i koji ste primili. Sadržaj aranžmana Organizator će ostvariti u potpunosti i na opisani način, osim u slučaju izuzetnih okolnosti (rat, nemiri, štrajkovi, terorističke akcije, sanitarni poremećaji, elementarne nepogode, intervencije nadležnih vlasti, kašnjenja prijevoznih sredstava, epidemije i pandemije).</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;font-weight:bold;vertical-align:baseline;\">2. Prijave i uplate</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;vertical-align:baseline;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;background-color:#ffffff;vertical-align:baseline;\">Prijave za putovanje primaju se preko web stanice ili direktno na račun Organizatora putovanja. Prilikom prijave Putnik je dužan dati točne osobne podatke svih putnika, tj. osoba upisanih u rezervaciji onako kako su isti upisani u putnim ispravama koje će putnici koristiti tijekom putovanja, tj. konzumacije rezervacije i pravodobno dostaviti svu dokumentaciju potrebnu za organiziranje putovanja, sve sukladno Uredbi Europskog parlamenta i Vijeća od 27.04.2016. godine o zaštiti pojedinaca u vezi s obradom osobnih podataka i o slobodnom kretanju i Zakona o provedbi Opće uredbe o zaštiti podataka. Organizator kao turistička agencija jamči da će sve isprave i važeće podatke potrebne za nesmetanu realizaciju putovanja upotrebljavati sukladno zakonskim regulativama koje proizlaze iz Ugovora i Općih uvjeta. Organizator nije odgovoran za korištenje ili prosljeđivanje netočnih ili nepotpunih osobnih podataka osoba upisanih u rezervaciji, te će sve troškove nastale zbog netočnih ili nepotpunih osobnih podataka osoba upisanih u rezervaciji podmiriti Putnik.</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;vertical-align:baseline;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;background-color:#ffffff;vertical-align:baseline;\">Prilikom prijave za grupna putovanja Putnik uplaćuje 30% vrijednosti aranžmana, te je preostali iznos dužan uplatiti 45 dana prije samog putovanja ukoliko nije drugačije navedeno. Prilikom prijave za individualna putovanja Putnik jednokratno uplaćuje cjelokupni iznos aranžmana sukladno naznačenim rokovima.</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;vertical-align:baseline;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;background-color:#ffffff;vertical-align:baseline;\">Na dan prijave Putnik potpisuje ugovor pod naznakom “Upoznat sam s programom i uvjetima putovanja te ih u cijelosti prihvaćam. Potvrđujem da mi je ponuđeno putno osiguranje.” Na taj način sve što je navedeno u ovim uvjetima postaje pravna obveza i za Putnika i za Organizatora.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;font-weight:bold;vertical-align:baseline;\">3. Sadržaj i cijena aranžmana</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;vertical-align:baseline;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;background-color:#ffffff;vertical-align:baseline;\">Sadržaj aranžmana čini, odnosno cijena aranžmana uključuje, sve što je Organizator putovanja naveo u programu putovanja. Posebne usluge su usluge koje nisu uključene u cijenu aranžmana pa ih stoga Putnik posebno plaća. Ove se usluge trebaju zatražiti prilikom prijave i doplaćuju se na cijenu aranžmana. Fakultativne i posebne usluge koje putnik zatraži tijekom trajanja putovanja plaćaju se turističkom pratitelju ili predstavniku Organizatora putovanja u valuti zemlje u kojoj se usluga pruža. Cijene aranžmana objavljene su u eurima, a izračunate prema cijenama usluga u referentnim valutama po prodajnom tečaju poslovne banke Organizatora putovanja na određeni dan.</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;vertical-align:baseline;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;background-color:#ffffff;vertical-align:baseline;\">Organizator zadržava pravo promjene objavljenih cijena u slučaju promjene cijena smještaja, prehrane, prijevoznih i drugih usluga, odnosno u slučaju promjene vrijednosnog odnosa valuta koje su osnova za izračunavanje cijene aranžmana. Za povišenje cijene aranžmana i dodatnih sadržaja do 8% nije potrebna suglasnost Putnika (povećanje se obračunava na sve dijelove uplate). U slučaju povišenja većeg od 8%, Putnik ima pravo raskinuti ugovor bez obveze na nadoknadu štete.</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;vertical-align:baseline;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;background-color:#ffffff;vertical-align:baseline;\">U slučaju nepopunjenih, a zakupljenih kapaciteta na pojedinim aranžmanima, Organizator zadržava pravo korekcije cijene i primijeniti posebne marketinške akcije u svrhu lakše prodaje nepopunjenih kapaciteta. Putnici koji su uplatili aranžman po punoj cijeni nemaju pravo na povrat razlike cijene aranžmana.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;font-weight:bold;vertical-align:baseline;\">4. Kategorizacija i opis usluga</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;vertical-align:baseline;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;background-color:#ffffff;vertical-align:baseline;\">Ponuđeni smještajni objekti, restorani, prijevozna sredstva i dr. opisani su prema službenoj kategorizaciji mjesne turističke organizacije u vrijeme izdavanja programa. Standardi smještaja, prehrane, usluga i dr. pojedinih mjesta su različiti i nisu usporedivi. Organizator ne preuzima odgovornost za usmenu ili pismenu informaciju koja nije u skladu s opisom usluga i objekata u objavljenim programima, a koja je dobivena od strane treće osobe. Ako putnik koristi trokrevetnu ili četverokrevetnu sobu u hotelu, hotelijer najčešće daje dvokrevetnu sobu s pomoćnim ležajem ili sobu s dva bračna kreveta za smještaj 4 osobe. Kvaliteta pomoćnog (dodatnog) ležaja u potpunosti ovisi o hotelu. Organizator ni u kojem slučaju ne snosi odgovornost po pitanju kvalitete pomoćnog ležaja, pa eventualno nezadovoljstvo putnika proizašlo iz ovih razloga ne može biti predmetom prigovora.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;font-weight:bold;vertical-align:baseline;\">5. Promjena programa</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;vertical-align:baseline;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;background-color:#ffffff;vertical-align:baseline;\">Organizator putovanja ima pravo promijeniti program ako nastupe izvanredne okolnosti (otkazi, kašnjenja, izmjene lokalnih agencija) koje se ne mogu predvidjeti, izbjeći ili otkloniti, te će se smatrati da je program ispunjen u cijelosti ako do kraja putovanja bude izveden. Tijekom putovanja, raspored obilaska je podložan promjenama prema procjeni pratitelja. Ugovoreni smještaj može se zamijeniti samo smještajem u objektu iste ili više kategorije, a na teret Organizatora, te će se isti smatrati da je proveden u cijelosti. Ako izmjene ugovora o putovanju u paket-aranžmanu ili zamjenskom paket-aranžmanu imaju za posijedicu paket-aranžman niže kvalitete ili cijene, putnik ima pravo na primjereno sniženje cijene.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;font-weight:bold;vertical-align:baseline;\">6. Pravo Organizatora na otkaz</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;vertical-align:baseline;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;background-color:#ffffff;vertical-align:baseline;\">Organizator može raskinuti ugovor o putovanju u paket-aranžmanu prije početka paket-aranžmana i putniku u cijelosti vratiti sva plaćanja primljena za paket-aranžman, bez obveze naknade štete putniku:</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;vertical-align:baseline;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;background-color:#ffffff;vertical-align:baseline;\">– ako Organizatora u izvršenju ugovora spriječe izvanredne okolnosti koje se nisu mogle izbjeći te ako Putnika o raskidu ugovora obavijesti bez nepotrebnog odgađanja prije početka paket-aranžmana.</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;vertical-align:baseline;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;background-color:#ffffff;vertical-align:baseline;\">– ako je broj osoba koje su prijavljene za paket-aranžman manji od najmanjeg broja navedenog u ugovoru i ako organizator obavijesti putnika o raskidu ugovora unutar roka utvrđenog u ugovoru, ali ne kasnije od najmanje 20 dana prije početka paket-aranžmana.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;font-weight:bold;vertical-align:baseline;\">7. Odustajanje Putnika od putovanja</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;vertical-align:baseline;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;background-color:#ffffff;vertical-align:baseline;\">Putnik ima pravo na usmeni ili pismeni otkaz putovanja prije početka putovanja u prodajnom mjestu gdje je prijavio putovanje. Organizator u tom slučaju ima pravo na naknadu troškova zbog otkazanog putovanja, a visina troškova određuje se prema danu Putnikova otkazivanja i vrsti putovanja. Zbog svega navedenog Organizator predlaže uplatu putnog osiguranja. Ukoliko Putnik otkaže uplaćeni aranžman, Organizator od ukupne cijene aranžmana zadržava:</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;font-weight:bold;vertical-align:baseline;\">Daleka putovanja (izvan Europe):</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;vertical-align:baseline;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;background-color:#ffffff;vertical-align:baseline;\">– za otkaz do 180 dana prije polaska: 20%</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;vertical-align:baseline;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;background-color:#ffffff;vertical-align:baseline;\">– za otkaz 179-90 dana prije polaska: 70%</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;vertical-align:baseline;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;background-color:#ffffff;vertical-align:baseline;\">– za otkaz 89-0 dana prije polaska i nakon polaska: 100%</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;text-align:justify;margin-top:14pt;margin-bottom:18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;font-weight:bold;vertical-align:baseline;\">Individualna putovanja, avio karte i rezervacije smještaja: </span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;text-align:justify;margin-top:14pt;margin-bottom:18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;vertical-align:baseline;\">–  Ukoliko Putnik otkaže individualni paket aranžman koji uključuje avio kartu i smještaj, organizator od ukupne cijene aranžmana na ime naknade štete zadržava 100 % iznosa cijene avio karte (osim ako u uvjetima tarife avio karte nije navedeno drugačije) bez obzira na vrijeme do početka putovanja, a za otkaz hotela i drugih usluga vrijede uvjeti dobavljača, osim kada je usluga rezervirana pod posebnim uvjetima koji ne dozvoljavaju povrat (tzv. non-refundable) kada pružatelj usluge zadržava 100 % iznosa predmetne usluge.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;text-align:justify;margin-top:14pt;margin-bottom:18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;vertical-align:baseline;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;vertical-align:baseline;\">Organizator je dužan brinuti o provedbi usluga kao i izboru izvršitelja usluga pažnjom dobrog organizatora te brinuti o pravima i interesima Putnika suglasno dobrim običajima u turizmu. Organizator je dužan Putniku pružiti sve navedene usluge za pojedini aranžman u programu i odgovara Putniku zbog možebitnog neizvršenja usluga ili dijela usluga. Organizator isključuje svaku odgovornost u slučaju promjena i neizvršenja usluga prouzročenih višom silom (članak 1.) te zbog kašnjenja prijevoznih sredstava za koje prijevoznik ne odgovara prema pozitivnim propisima i međunarodnim konvencijama. U ovim slučajevima Putnik podmiruje sve dodatne troškove.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;font-weight:bold;vertical-align:baseline;\">9. Obveze Putnika</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;vertical-align:baseline;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;background-color:#ffffff;vertical-align:baseline;\">Putnik je dužan:</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;vertical-align:baseline;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;background-color:#ffffff;vertical-align:baseline;\">Posjedovati valjane putne isprave, te dostaviti imena i prezimena ista kao iz dokumenta (putovnice) s kojim putuje. Na zahtjev Organizatora Putnik je dužan dostaviti kopiju ili original važeće putovnice koju koristi tijekom putovanja. Za naknadne izmjene ili dodavanje prezimena Putnik sam snosi troškove promjene i izmjena istih. Za daleka putovanja (izvan Europe) putovnica mora vrijediti minimalno još 6 mjeseci od samog ulaska u zemlju. Troškove gubitka ili krađe dokumenata tijekom putovanja snosi Putnik. Pratitelj ili predstavnik Organizatora će pomoći, ali uz uvjet da se program neometano odvija. Ako je za neko putovanje potrebna viza, Organizator putovanja može, na zahtjev Putnika, kada je to moguće, uz nadoplatu posredovati u njenom pribavljanju. Organizator putovanja ne jamči ishođenje viza, te ne odgovara za ispravnost istih.</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;vertical-align:baseline;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;background-color:#ffffff;vertical-align:baseline;\">Cijepiti se i posjedovati potvrde i dokumente o cijepljenju za putovanja u zemlje za koje je ono potrebno prema propisima Svjetske zdravstvene organizacije. U tom slučaju Putnik prilaže liječničku potvrdu. Neposjedovanje ovih dokumenata kao i/ili neispravnost putnih isprava koji dovedu do odustajanja od putovanja ili nemogućnosti nastavka putovanja ne obvezuju Organizatora putovanja te se obračunavaju otkazni troškovi iz članka 7.</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;vertical-align:baseline;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;background-color:#ffffff;vertical-align:baseline;\">Poštivati carinske i devizne propise Republike Hrvatske, kao i država u kojima boravi tijekom putovanja.</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;vertical-align:baseline;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;background-color:#ffffff;vertical-align:baseline;\">Pridržavati se kućnog reda u svim posjećenim objektima te surađivati s izvršiteljima usluga u dobroj namjeri.</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;vertical-align:baseline;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;background-color:#ffffff;vertical-align:baseline;\">Pridržavati se naputaka i surađivati s Organizatorom, turističkim pratiteljem i/ili predstavnikom Organizatora, prilikom polaska na putovanje turističkom pratitelju odnosno predstavniku Organizatora predočiti dokument o plaćenom aranžmanu (original voucher, potvrdu o uplati, kopiju virmana).</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;vertical-align:baseline;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;background-color:#ffffff;vertical-align:baseline;\">Zatražiti i provjeriti svu dostavljenu putnu dokumentaciju (avio karte, vouchere za hotele, police osiguranja, termine za transfere…). Ukoliko Organizator ne dobije unutar 24h (ili prema ponudi) od dostave dokumenata napomenu od strane Putnika, smatrat će se da je sva poslana dokumentacija valjana i ispravna, te sav trošak promjena i izmjena snosi Putnik.</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;vertical-align:baseline;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;background-color:#ffffff;vertical-align:baseline;\">U slučajevima nepoštivanja ovih obveza, Putnik odgovara Organizatoru za učinjenu štetu.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br /><br /></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;font-weight:bold;vertical-align:baseline;\">10. Prtljaga</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;vertical-align:baseline;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;background-color:#ffffff;vertical-align:baseline;\">Ukoliko u programu putovanja nije drugačije navedeno, Putnik ima pravo na besplatan prijevoz do 15 kg prtljage na čarterskim letovima te do 20 kg prtljage na redovitim zračnim linijama. Djeca do 2 godine nemaju pravo na besplatan prijevoz prtljage. Prtljaga se prevozi na Putnikov rizik, stoga se preporuča osiguranje prtljage kod osiguravajućeg društva. Organizator putovanja nije odgovoran za uništenu ni izgubljenu prtljagu, kao ni za krađu prtljage ili dragocjenosti u hotelu (preporuča se najam sefa), prijevoznim sredstvima. Prijavu za oštećenu ili izgubljenu prtljagu Putnik upućuje prijevozniku ili recepciji smještajnog objekta, ovisno gdje su oštećenje ili gubitak nastupili.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;font-weight:bold;vertical-align:baseline;\">11. Putno osiguranje</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;vertical-align:baseline;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;background-color:#ffffff;vertical-align:baseline;\">Djelatnici agencije u kojoj se uplaćuje aranžman obvezni su putniku ponuditi “paket” putnog osiguranja koji se sastoji od zdravstvenog osiguranja putnika tijekom boravka u inozemstvu te osiguranja prtljage, osiguranja od posljedica nesretnog slučaja kao i osiguranja od rizika Putnikovog otkaza putovanja, koji se nude kako za putovanja po inozemstvu tako i po našoj zemlji. Polica osiguranja od rizika Putnikovog otkaza putovanja mora biti izdana najkasnije 48 sati od prve uplate. Prihvaćanjem ugovora o putovanju, koji čine i ovi uvjeti putovanja, Putnik potvrđuje da mu je bio ponuđen “paket” putnih osiguranja. Organizator je posrednik prilikom ugovaranja police osiguranja, te u slučaju potraživanja od osiguravajuće kuće ne može utjecati na ishod.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;font-weight:bold;vertical-align:baseline;\">12. Smještaj u sobe/apartmane</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;vertical-align:baseline;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;background-color:#ffffff;vertical-align:baseline;\">Ako Putnik nije izričito ugovorio sobu/apartman s posebnim odlikama, prihvatit će bilo koju službeno registriranu sobu/apartman za izdavanje u dotičnom objektu, opisanu u katalogu i cjeniku. Ako je moguće, Organizator će pokušati zadovoljiti Putnikov dodatni zahtjev za smještajem (komfor, orijentacija sobe, kat i sl.), ali ne može jamčiti ispunjenje takvog zahtjeva</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;font-weight:bold;vertical-align:baseline;\">13. Putovanja u organizaciji drugih organizatora/turoperatora</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;vertical-align:baseline;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:#222222;background-color:#ffffff;vertical-align:baseline;\">Za sve aranžmane gdje je glavni organizator Desert Road for Tourism vrijede ovi Opći uvjeti, osim u slučajevima gdje je Desert Road for Tourism posrednik, odnosno nije glavni organizator putovanja. Za takve aranžmane u Ugovoru će biti naznačen odgovorni organizator te se za to putovanje primjenjuju opći uvjeti odgovornog organizatora i Desert Road for Tourism ne odgovara za provedbu turističkih aranžmana drugih organizatora. Potpisivanjem ugovora Putni</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Open Sans\', sans-serif;color:#222222;background-color:#ffffff;vertical-align:baseline;\">k u cijelosti prihvaća program i uvjete putovanja.</span></p>', NULL, 1, NULL, '2023-09-07 10:48:47', '2023-09-07 10:48:47'),
(10, 16, 'en', 'About Us', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.295;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:8pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Welcome to Desert Road Adventure Tourism Agency, where our journey began in the heart of Egypt. We aim to provide you with an extraordinary experience of Egypt. Our team is led by a passionate traveler with years of exploration under her belt, who has made Egypt her home for quite some time now. Her love for this incredible country is so infectious that she\'s eager to share it with fellow travelers like you. What fuels her is the belief that every individual deserves a travel adventure they\'ll cherish for a lifetime. We don\'t just offer \"typical tours\" – we create fresh, unforgettable experiences. So, are you ready to embark on an incredible adventure with us?</span></p>\n<h1 style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0.5rem;font-weight:500;line-height:1.2;font-size:2.5rem;color:#999971;font-family:Poppins, sans-serif;background-color:#ffffff;\">Clients:</h1>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.295;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:8pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">At Desert Road, we consider our clients as cherished friends. You can place your complete trust in us because we only partner with businesses that share our unwavering commitment to quality. While our offerings include trips from renowned tour operators, we\'re more than willing to go the extra mile to craft a journey that\'s uniquely tailored to your dreams.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.295;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:8pt;\"> </p>\n<h1 style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0.5rem;font-weight:500;line-height:1.2;font-size:2.5rem;color:#999971;font-family:Poppins, sans-serif;background-color:#ffffff;\">Mission:</h1>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.295;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:8pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Our mission is to make your travel dreams come true. Our knowledgeable team is here to help you choose the perfect journey that aligns with your interests and desires. We\'re here to offer you a lavish and adventurous experience while introducing you to fellow travelers. Our goal is to create a joyful atmosphere for satisfied clients and partners who will keep coming back for more.</span></p>\n<h1 style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0.5rem;font-weight:500;line-height:1.2;font-size:2.5rem;color:#999971;font-family:Poppins, sans-serif;background-color:#ffffff;\">Vision:</h1>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.295;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:8pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">We aspire to be your trusted travel companion, ready to assist you in every way possible. Through our efforts, we aim to draw in travelers from the Balkan region and reveal the captivating beauty of Egypt firsthand. Based on the values that guide our work, we\'ve brought together top-quality tourism services, offering them under the most favorable conditions. You\'ll always find a warm and professional welcome from our staff. We firmly believe that traveling is a transformational journey, one that enriches our knowledge and deepens our understanding of the world around us.</span></p>', NULL, 1, 1, '2023-09-07 10:50:50', '2023-09-18 16:27:04'),
(11, 16, 'hr', 'O nama', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.295;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:8pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Dobrodošli u Agenciju za pustolovni turizam Desert Road, gdje je naša priča započela u srcu Egipta. Cilj nam je pružiti vam izvanredno iskustvo Egipta. Naš tim predvodi strastveni putnik s godinama istraživanja, koji je već neko vrijeme svoj dom pronašao upravo ovdje u Egiptu. Njena ljubav prema ovom nevjerojatnom kraju toliko je zarazna da želi podijeliti isto oduševljenje s putnicima poput vas. Ono što je pokreće je vjera da svaki pojedinac zaslužuje putničku avanturu koju će čuvati cijelog života. Ne nudimo samo \"obične ture\" - stvaramo svježa i nezaboravna iskustva. Dakle, jeste li spremni krenuti na nevjerojatnu avanturu s nama?</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.295;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:8pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Klijenti:</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.295;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:8pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">U Agenciji Desert Road, smatramo naše klijente dragim prijateljima. Možete imati potpuno povjerenje u nas jer surađujemo samo s poslovnim partnerima koji dijele našu nepokolebljivu predanost kvaliteti. Iako naša ponuda uključuje putovanja renomiranih turoperatora, spremni smo ići korak dalje kako bismo stvorili putovanje koje je jedinstveno prilagođeno vašim snovima.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.295;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:8pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Misija:</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.295;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:8pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Naša misija je ostvariti vaše putničke snove. Naš stručni tim ovdje je da vam pomogne odabrati savršeno putovanje koje se uklapa u vaše interese i želje. Tu smo da vam ponudimo raskošno i pustolovno iskustvo, dok vas upoznajemo s drugim putnicima. Naš cilj je stvoriti veselu atmosferu za zadovoljne klijente i partnere koji će se uvijek vraćati po još.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.295;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:8pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Vizija:</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.295;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:8pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.295;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:8pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Težimo biti vaš pouzdani putnički partner, spreman pomoći vam na svaki mogući način. Kroz naše napore, cilj nam je privući putnike iz Balkanske regije i otkriti vam fascinantnu ljepotu Egipta iz prve ruke. Temeljeći se na vrijednostima koje vode naš rad, okupili smo vrhunske turističke usluge, nudeći ih pod najpovoljnijim uvjetima. Naš tim uvijek će vas srdačno i profesionalno dočekati. Snažno vjerujemo da je putovanje transformacijsko iskustvo koje obogaćuje naše znanje i produbljuje naše razumijevanje svijeta oko nas.</span></p>', NULL, 1, 1, '2023-09-07 10:51:27', '2023-09-18 16:27:30');
